extendedInfo.description: It's here! Download the new based on My Little Pony game from Google Play.This game will put all your brony knowledge to the test so you'll remember all those moments from the show that you didn't even remember to guess who is the pony whose cutie mark is on screen. -Once you beat the game you can reset the database from the options menu to start again.-As you guess who is the pony whose cutie mark is on screen a list of the cutie marks you have been guessing will be saved so you will be able to see the name of each guessed pony with its cutie mark.-There is also an emal FAQ section that tries to solve all your questions. If it doesn't solve your questions send an email to phoeps@gmail.com and I'll answer as soon as possible.ATTENTION!-All the introduced names will be accepted only in small latin letters.END USER LICENSE AGREEMENT================================================== ==========All content, copyrights and trademarks belong to their respective owners. This is an unofficial My Little Pony application and it is not approved, endorsed, associated or connected with game creators. We do not own any copyrights, trademarks or content in this application, neither we use any illegal information.  IF YOU ARE A COPYRIGHT OWNER and you feel that our application violates your terms, please contact us first before submitting complaint to Google Play - we always willing to cooperate with you and we will make all required changes or remove the application.
